creator: Milkywire
descriptionHtml:
A new digital platform for everyone who wants to do something for the planet and the people fighting for it. Milkywire is a new type of platform for impact that connects people who want to change the world directly with the best grassroots NGOs around the world doing real work in the field.

By downloading the Milkywire app, you can easily find, fund and follow so called impacters - screened grassroots NGOs from around the world working to fight extinction, save our oceans, clean the planet, protect and restore forests and more. Support local projects directly and see proof of impact by following their progress through weekly video updates directly on the app.

SCREENED GRASSROOTS NGOs
Change starts at the grassroots – with impacters and local projects. We handpick and screen all impacters and their organizations, and the impacters currently on the platform are some of the best grassroots NGOs in the world.

FIND CAUSES THAT MATTER
Discover and explore impacters that fight extinction, protect forests and plant trees, save our oceans and its wildlife, clean the planet and build communities that use resources sustainably.

FUND LOCAL CHANGE, DIRECTLY
Let Milkywire decide where your contribution is most needed and five impacters for you to support are selected, or save the world by contributing to an entire cause in one go or individual impacters one by one. You decide how your donation is spent.

FOLLOW THE WORK
We connect you with the ones making a difference. Follow the work and progress through weekly video updates directly from impacters, ask them questions by commenting on their posts, or show them some love through reactions as they’re working hard to save the planet.

We want to change the way charity works. On Milkywire, you’re not just donating to charity. You’re part of the work, the progress and you get a genuine, ongoing connection to the best grassroots NGOs around the world doing real work in the field.

Get the app. Make an impact.


Causes that Milkywire support:
Conservation of lions, cheetahs, leopards, tigers, rhinos, elephants, turtles, sharks, orcas, wild dogs, spotted hyena, amphibians, reptiles, fishing cats, snow leopard, red pandas, humpback whales, dolphins, snakes, bees, Amur tiger, beetles, insects, pangolins, seals, forests, coral reefs, anteaters, marine mammals and mitigating the human-wildlife conflict. As well as causes regarding access to water, polar ice research, air pollution reduction, tree planting, beach clean-up, plastic pollution reduction, disentanglement, ghost nets, and wildlife trafficking.

A new digital platform for everyone who wants to do something for the planet and the people fighting for it. Milkywire is a new type of platform for impact that connects people who want to change the world directly with the best grassroots NGOs around the world doing real work in the field.

By downloading the Milkywire app, you can easily find, fund and follow so called impacters - screened grassroots NGOs from around the world working to fight extinction, save our oceans, clean the planet, protect and restore forests and more. Support local projects directly and see proof of impact by following their progress through weekly video updates directly on the app.

SCREENED GRASSROOTS NGOs
Change starts at the grassroots – with impacters and local projects. We handpick and screen all impacters and their organizations, and the impacters currently on the platform are some of the best grassroots NGOs in the world.

FIND CAUSES THAT MATTER
Discover and explore impacters that fight extinction, protect forests and plant trees, save our oceans and its wildlife, clean the planet and build communities that use resources sustainably.

FUND LOCAL CHANGE, DIRECTLY
Let Milkywire decide where your contribution is most needed and five impacters for you to support are selected, or save the world by contributing to an entire cause in one go or individual impacters one by one. You decide how your donation is spent.

FOLLOW THE WORK
We connect you with the ones making a difference. Follow the work and progress through weekly video updates directly from impacters, ask them questions by commenting on their posts, or show them some love through reactions as they’re working hard to save the planet.

We want to change the way charity works. On Milkywire, you’re not just donating to charity. You’re part of the work, the progress and you get a genuine, ongoing connection to the best grassroots NGOs around the world doing real work in the field.

Get the app. Make an impact.


Causes that Milkywire support:
Conservation of lions, cheetahs, leopards, tigers, rhinos, elephants, turtles, sharks, orcas, wild dogs, spotted hyena, amphibians, reptiles, fishing cats, snow leopard, red pandas, humpback whales, dolphins, snakes, bees, Amur tiger, beetles, insects, pangolins, seals, forests, coral reefs, anteaters, marine mammals and mitigating the human-wildlife conflict. As well as causes regarding access to water, polar ice research, air pollution reduction, tree planting, beach clean-up, plastic pollution reduction, disentanglement, ghost nets, and wildlife trafficking.

title: Milkywire – Make an impact

creator: Milkywire
descriptionHtml:
A new, easy way to help save the planet. Milkywire lets you support impactful grassroots organizations worldwide and see how your donation makes a difference via updates directly from the people in the field.

Milkywire is your personal way to make a change, it’s a platform that helps you maximize your giving power and allows you to get closer and see your impact.

Supporting the United Nations Global Goals.
Donating to organizations on Milkywire means you’re directly supporting charities that help the environment. All working in line with the Biosphere Goals, #6 Clean Water and Sanitation, #13 Climate Action, #14 Life below Water, and #15 Life on Land.

Make an impact in three easy steps:

CHOOSE CAUSES YOU CARE ABOUT
Browse causes and award-winning organizations working in the field to protect, restore and save the planet. Click the heart icon throughout the app to add them to your support list.

BECOME A MONTHLY SUPPORTER
Skip a coffee per month and join us to make a positive impact on the planet. Give directly to all the causes in your support list. Change the amount whenever you want.

FOLLOW THE WORK IN THE FIELD
Get updates directly from impacters you support and see the work you’re enabling in real time. Ask questions, learn from the experts and show your appreciation.

Help save the planet with an app. Organizations, environmental nonprofits and charities, all in one place, working to help the earth.

Take action for our planet. Make an impact. Get the app.
